Get win probability chart data from API

cfb_metrics_wp.Rd

Get win probability chart data from API

cfb_metrics_wp(game_id, adjust_for_spread = TRUE)

Arguments

game_id

(Integer required): Game ID filter for querying a single game Can be found using the `cfb_game_info()` function
adjust_for_spread

(Logical default TRUE): Toggles pre-game spread adjustments

Examples


cfb_metrics_wp(game_id = 401012356)
